Sounds like a match!  But what is going to happen to them?  What can they possibly do with their lives if they live in a virtual world?  I sure as heck am not going to support him! 
 
Bryn won't be inclined to change servers.  He is on Karana.  58 druid.  Maybe we can get them both to start characters on the same server, pref. one that one of us is on!  <G>

Seriously, my 17 yr old son appears to have a much brighter future.  He took 7th place in the state FBLA competition in Technology Concepts AND he likes wearing a suit!  <G>  He has a 53 Necro on Karana.
